2) Community Testing Program
We encourage our users to report issues, bugs or problems found on the Testnet. The program is suitable for non-technical users, so don’t worry if you are not a hacker.

The following rewards will be provided for reporting valid issues:

Low severity issues: 100 VRSW
Mid severity issues: 250 VRSW
High severity issues: 500 VRSW
In total, up to 10,000 VRSW will be distributed in this activity.

Only valid reports will be considered.

In case several people report the same issue, only the first reporter will be rewarded.

The validity and severity of reported issues will be determined solely by our development team. The team’s decisions will be final.

The bugs should be reported through this form.
